re real ,but many details on Buddhism  have been lost because of errors in descending and translation.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>2.çœŸå¾‹:&lt;&lt;äº”åˆ†å¾‹&gt;&gt;æœ€æ¥è¿‘åŸå§‹å¾‹è—.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>2.Real vinaya:<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>The Five-category Vinaya is nearest to the primitive Vinay.

